name: Snowflake Kiss
description:
A Black-Capped Chickadee with snowflakes on its beak braces against a snowy gust of wind on a bright sunny day.

2017. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

Birb Series: Part 1 - Chickadee III
